<% content_for :title, "AI Sketch to 3D Rendering & Photorealistic Design" %>

<% content_for :description, "Convert hand-drawn or architectural sketches into stunning 3D photorealistic renderings instantly. Visualize concepts with high fidelity and full editing control." %>

<% content_for :keywords, "AI sketch to 3D rendering, 2D drawing to photorealism AI, AI 3D reconstruction from sketch, neural network 3D modeling landscape, rapid prototyping landscape design, concept visualization tool, AI CAD alternative for landscape, convert architectural blueprint to 3D rendering, photorealistic garden rendering from sketch, convert hand-drawn plan to 3D" %>

