        conceptualization and final visualization, offering a powerful
        alternative to complex and time-consuming traditional CAD and 3D
        modeling software.
      </p>

      <div
        class="
          flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 animate-fade-in-up
          delay-300
        "
      >
        <%= link_to "Try Sketch to 3D Free", new_user_registration_path, class: "px-8 py-4 bg-accent text-black font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,172,193,0.4)]" %>
        <%= link_to "See How It Works", "#how-it-works", class: "px-8 py-4 bg-transparent border border-white/30 text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm" %>
