              </p>
            </div>

            <%# Feature Item %>
            <div
              class="
                group p-5 rounded-2xl bg-neutral-800/30 border
                border-white/5 hover:border-accent/30 transition-colors
              "
            >
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-secondary"></span>
                Dynamic View Options
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 pl-4 border-l border-white/10 ml-1">
                The resulting 3D rendering can be fully manipulated. It can be
                converted into the high-angle Drone View and allows for camera
                rotations and mask edits, enabling you to examine your sketched
                design from any perspective.
              </p>
